sequenceDiagram
autonumber
participant Scope as LayerInstallerBase
participant Bootstrap as BootstrapAssetInstaller
participant P as IAssetProvider(s)
participant R as IAssetRegistrar(s)
participant G as IAddressablesGateway
participant H as IAssetReferenceHandler
participant C as IAddressablesAssetClient
participant Child as Child IContainerBuilder

Scope->>Bootstrap: InitializeAsync(resolver)
Scope->>Bootstrap: OnCompletedAsync(resolver)
Bootstrap->>P: PreloadAsync(ct)
P->>G: LoadAsync<T>(reference/label)
G->>H: AcquireAsync / AcquireByTypeAsync
H->>C: LoadAssetAsync / ResolveLabelAsync
C-->>H: UnityEngine.Object
H-->>G: IAssetHandle<T>
G-->>P: loaded handle
P-->>Bootstrap: provider loaded (local cached state)

Scope->>Bootstrap: ConfigureChildBuilder(child,...)
Bootstrap->>R: Register(childBuilder)
R->>Child: RegisterInstance<T>(typed asset)
